reviewText: In this film there's not much of a story. As a matter of fact at the end of the second 30 minute installment it promises to have a continuation, yet there isn't one. It's a typical high school anime with one exception...it has some seriously over exaggerated sex scenes. Plenty of high pitched moaning and sudden confrontations where two characters start doing it with little regard to their surroundings.The biggest flaw is the lack of a major plot. The plot is so thin I can barely remember what the subject was. Basically a theater group full of misfits and weirdoes in 2-b are trying to prove themselves to be otherwise, but the story is so foggy that after an hour, you're promised more and are given nothing leaving you hanging. The sex scenes were little more than repeat animations, high moans, and over exaggerated wetness. Little substance at all, but the main idea is the sex scenes. As a matter of fact the sudden sex scenes made me wish for more plot along the way.
Title: N/A
